      "path": "audio/narrations/double-pendulum/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "这是一个双摆，只是在普通单摆下面又挂了一根摆杆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "double-pendulum",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/double-pendulum/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "结构简单到不能再简单，运动却复杂到几乎无法预测。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "double-pendulum",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/double-pendulum/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "它是研究确定性混沌最经典的力学模型之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "double-pendulum",
      "section_id": "equations",
      "line_id": "eq-1",
      "filename": "equations-eq-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/double-pendulum/equations-eq-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "双摆只有两个自由度，就是上下两根杆各自的摆角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "double-pendulum",
      "section_id": "equations",
      "line_id": "eq-2",
      "filename": "equations-eq-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/double-pendulum/equations-eq-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "用拉格朗日力学，可以推出两个摆角的角加速度方程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "double-pendulum",
      "section_id": "equations",
      "line_id": "eq-3",
      "filename": "equations-eq-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/double-pendulum/equations-eq-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "这两个方程彼此耦合，而且高度非线性，没有简洁的解析解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "double-pendulum",
      "section_id": "equations",
      "line_id": "eq-4",
      "filename": "equations-eq-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/double-pendulum/equations-eq-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "所以我们用四阶龙格库塔方法，一步一步在计算机里把它积分出来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "double-pendulum",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-1",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/double-pendulum/chaos-chaos-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "让两个几乎一模一样的双摆同时释放，初始角度只差万分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "double-pendulum",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-2",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/double-pendulum/chaos-chaos-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "起初它们的轨迹重合，可没过多久就彻底分道扬镳。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "double-pendulum",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-3",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/double-pendulum/chaos-chaos-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "这就是对初值的敏感依赖，也是蝴蝶效应的力学写照。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "double-pendulum",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/double-pendulum/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "切换不同的初始状态，从温和摆动到大角度的翻转狂舞。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "double-pendulum",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
